@Mnemosyne.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5226

### Create a memory
POST {{Mnemosyne.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/memory/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Example memory content",
  "type": 0
}

### Search memories
GET {{Mnemosyne.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/memory/search?q=example&topK=10

### Health - Liveness
GET {{Mnemosyne.Api_HostAddress}}/health/live

### Health - Readiness
GET {{Mnemosyne.Api_HostAddress}}/health/ready
